   374	\subsection{Benchmark protocol}
   375	
   376	The empirical benchmark reports eight regression variants and one selected
   377	classification variant.  All paired comparisons reported below are computed
   378	on the strict intersection $N_{\cap}=32$ of cohort rows available for every
   379	paper variant, so that ratios and win counts are directly comparable across
   380	variant pairs.  The classification cohort contains 17 manifest rows, with 13
   381	paired datasets for the selected classifier.
   382	
   383	\begin{table}[t]
