   405	(\texttt{AOM-compact-cv5}), AOM-PLS (best)
   406	(\texttt{ASLS-AOM-compact-cv5}), Ridge-default
   407	(\texttt{ridge-default-cv5}), Ridge-HPO
   408	(\texttt{ridge-tabpfn-hpo-60trials}), AOM-Ridge (simple)
   409	(\texttt{AOMRidge-global-compact-none}) and AOM-Ridge (best)
