One-shot screening of linear preprocessing operators
  for PLS and Ridge calibration in near-infrared
                   spectroscopy
                    Grégory Beurier1,2        Robin Reiter1,2       Camille Noûs3
                               Lauriane Rouan1,2        Denis Cornet1,2
                     1
                CIRAD, UMR AGAP Institut, Montpellier, France
2
    UMR AGAP Institut, Univ Montpellier, CIRAD, INRAE, Institut Agro, Montpellier,
                                      France
