482:7    POP-PLS Exploration
483:POP-PLS allows different operators across components, which is attractive as a modelling idea
484:but weak in the current regression benchmark. The two regression POP variants have median
485:ratios above 1.37 against PLS-standard and win on roughly one fifth of dataset/seed rows.
487:           Table 8: POP-PLS regression summary from the AOM-PLS seeds012 run.
