490: POP-simpls-covariance-numpy                            55    165                   1.385         33/165
493:    The poor POP regression result is consistent with a noisy component-wise selection sur-
494:face: extra flexibility increases variance without producing a stable aggregate gain. POP-style
495:classification rows are kept in the full classification table, but POP is not part of the main result.
